OL,3,CPeter Murrell to return to court after
OL,4,C#400,000 SNP embezzlement admission
OL,6,FFormer SNP chief executive Peter
OL,7,FMurrell is due to return to court for
OL,8,Fa further hearing, after he pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to embezzling more than
OL,10,F#400,000 from the party last week.
OL,12,FMurrell will appear at the High Court
OL,13,Fin Edinburgh, where prosecutors will
OL,14,Foutline the facts of the case.
OL,16,FJudge Lord Young will hear the
OL,17,Fprosecution "narrative" when the case
OL,18,Fcalls on Tuesday.
OL,26,@yD@MOUyD@WO]
