OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780473962
OL,3,CPeter Murrell to return to court after
OL,4,C#400,000 SNP embezzlement admission
OL,6,FSentencing of the 61-year-old, who is
OL,7,Fformer Scotland first minister Nicola
OL,8,FSturgeon's ex-husband, is due to take
OL,9,Fplace later in June.
OL,11,FOn Monday last week he admitted
OL,12,Fembezzling #400,310.65 from the SNP
OL,13,Fbetween August 2010 and October 2022.
OL,15,FCourt papers revealed a lengthy list
OL,16,Fof items he bought with the embezzled
OL,17,Fmoney, including a space telescope,
OL,18,FDVDs, a home library ladder worth more
OL,19,Fthan #900 and a coffee machine worth
OL,20,Fnearly #3,232.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780473962
OL,3,CPeter Murrell to return to court after
OL,4,C#400,000 SNP embezzlement admission
OL,6,FTwo cars and a #124,550 motorhome were
OL,7,Falso among the purchases.
OL,9,FMurrell's guilty plea has led to
OL,10,Fintense scrutiny for his former wife
OL,11,FMs Sturgeon, who has denied knowing of
OL,12,Fhis crimes ` saying she was "deceived,
OL,13,Fmisled and betrayed".
OL,15,FThe former SNP leader said she has
OL,16,Fbeen "completely exonerated" after a
OL,17,F"two-year-long, very forensic police
OL,18,Finvestigation" which saw police
OL,19,Fofficers search the home she and
OL,20,FMurrell had shared.
OL,26,@tD@]OUuD@TO]xD@FOUxD@\O]yD@AOUzD@NO]
