CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780473962
OL,3,CPeter Murrell to return to court after
OL,4,C#400,000 SNP embezzlement admission
OL,6,FMs Sturgeon was arrested and
OL,7,Fquestioned as part of the police
OL,8,Finvestigation into the SNP's finances,
OL,9,Fwhich was known as Operation
OL,10,FBranchform, but Police Scotland
OL,11,Fconfirmed she would face no action.
OL,13,FAt the weekend, the former first
OL,14,Fminister told the BBC's Sunday With
OL,15,FLaura Kuenssberg programme she feels
OL,16,Flike she is "serving a sentence for a
OL,17,Fcrime I did not commit".
OL,19,FMurrell's guilty plea has also led to
OL,20,Fcalls for an independent investigation
OL,21,Finto the SNP's finances.
OL,26,@xD@MOUyD@WO]
