PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780473962
OL,3,CPeter Murrell to return to court after
OL,4,C#400,000 SNP embezzlement admission
OL,6,FFormer first minister Lord Jack
OL,7,FMcConnell has said a joint inquiry by
OL,8,Fboth Holyrood and Westminster
OL,9,Fcommittees should examine Murrell's
OL,10,Fembezzlement.
OL,12,FShadow Scottish secretary Andrew Bowie
OL,13,Fhas called on Westminster's Scottish
OL,14,FAffairs Committee to initiate an
OL,15,Finquiry.
OL,17,FHowever current SNP leader and First
OL,18,FMinister John Swinney has said there
OL,19,Fis no need for such an inquiry,
OL,20,Femphasising the detailed nature of the
OL,21,Fpolice investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
