OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780473962
OL,3,CPeter Murrell to return to court after
OL,4,C#400,000 SNP embezzlement admission
OL,6,FHe told the Press Association last
OL,7,Fweek: "The police investigation has
OL,8,Fled to a criminal case.
OL,10,F"There has been a prosecution and
OL,11,Fthere has been a guilty plea and there
OL,12,Fwill be sentencing taking place as a
OL,13,Fconsequence.
OL,15,F"So, all these issues have been looked
OL,16,Fat.
OL,26,@oD@GOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
