OL,3,CPeter Murrell to return to court after
OL,4,C#400,000 SNP embezzlement admission
OL,6,F"We know what the problem was ` the
OL,7,Fproblem was criminal behaviour and the
OL,8,Fpolice have identified that and the
OL,9,Findividual involved has been
OL,10,Fprosecuted."
